comments.body:
This query fails with the same NullPointerException:

{code:SQL}
SELECT sys_created_on FROM servicenow_stg.sys_audit_distinct_tmp
WHERE unix_timestamp(sys_created_on) > unix_timestamp('2017-01-01 00:00:00')
{code}

It is surprising that this query does execute successfully:

{code:SQL}
SELECT sys_created_on FROM servicenow_stg.sys_audit_distinct_tmp
WHERE unix_timestamp(sys_created_on) > 1483246800
{code}

where {{1483246800}} is the output from {code:SQL} SELECT unix_timestamp('2017-01-01 00:00:00'){code}
